title: Sawbones: The Secret Life of Doctors
description:
Ever wonder what doctors do when they're not giving you a check up? Wonder how to get the most out of ever doctor's visit? We've got the answers for you in our new episode: The Secret Life of Doctors.

Music: "Medicines" by The Taxpayers
author: sawbones@maximumfun.org (Justin McElroy)
